1st type "echo "deb https://download.opensuse.org/repositories/home:/strycore/Debian_11/ ./" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/lutris.list" (this will get the parckage needed for the rest of the installment") now press enter
2nd type "wget -q https://download.opensuse.org/repositories/home:/strycore/Debian_11/Release.key -O- | sudo tee /etc/apt/trusted.gpg.d/lutris.asc" (this will get the package to install lutris) now press enter
3rd type "sudo apt update" (this will update the linux files and other important but dont need to know files" press enter now
4th type "sudo apt install lutris"" (this will install lutris) now press enter
